                         "VERSION CONTROL SYSTEM (VCS)
                                           VCS are software tools 
                                           VCS help software teams to  manage changes to source code over time.
                                           VCS  keeps track of every modification to the code in a special kind of database. 
                
                 For example,
                     > when you edit a file, [GIT CAN HELP TO DETERMINE EXACTLY]
                     > what changed, 
                     > who changed it, 
                     > and why.

